  "id": "RAW_655449a1",
  "title": "Gemini 应用现已支持生成交互式模拟和模型。",
  "url": "https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/gemini-app/3d-models-charts/",
  "date": "2026-04-09 16:00:00",
