  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"loader-mask\"></div>\n  <main id=\"jump-content\" class=\"site-content\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n   <div class=\"uni-layout-page uni-component-spacing short-post-page\">\n    <div class=\"short-post-page__grid\">\n     <div class=\"short-post-page__breadcrumb\">\n      <div class=\"breadcrumb__container\" data-component=\"uni-breadcrumb\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n       <button class=\"breadcrumb__prev-btn hide\" aria-label=\"Previous\"></button>\n       <button class=\"breadcrumb__next-btn hide\" aria-label=\"Next\"></button>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"short-post-page__post\">\n      <uni-short-post data-title=\"The Gemini app can now generate interactive simulations and models.\" author=\"\" author-job-title=\"\" author-url=\"\" date=\"Apr 09, 2026\" url=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/gemini-app/3d-models-charts/\" component-type=\"media_carousel\">\n       <!---->\n       <div class=\"short-post\">\n        <div class=\"short-post__header\">\n         <div class=\"uni-body--small short-post__date\">\n          <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n          Apr 09, 2026\n         </div>\n         <button tooltip=\"Copied\" aria-label=\"Copy to clipboard\" class=\"short-post__copy-link\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"social-link\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n        <!--?-->\n        <!--?-->\n        <p class=\"short-post__description\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Paragraph&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;The Gemini app can now generate interactive simulations and models.&quot;}\"><!--?lit$735867791$--></p>\n        <div slot=\"uni-short-post-description-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n         <div class=\"rich-text\">\n          <p data-block-key=\"9ro1x\">Gemini can transform your questions and complex topics into custom and interactive visualizations — directly within your chat.</p>\n          <p data-block-key=\"bnssp\">Previously, responses were largely just text with static diagrams. Now, we’re delivering functional simulations that can help you better understand the topic you’re asking Gemini about. Whether you’re rotating a molecule or simulating a complex physics system, you can explore further with just one prompt.</p>\n          <p data-block-key=\"8vtds\">When exploring how the moon orbits the Earth, you aren't stuck with a fixed diagram. You can manually adjust sliders or input exact numbers for initial velocity and gravity strength to instantly see how those specific variables create a stable orbit.</p>\n          <p data-block-key=\"1k2pr\">This feature is now rolling out globally to all Gemini app users. <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-1\" id=\"footnote-source-1\" aria-label=\"Jump to link reference 1\"> <sup>1</sup> </a> Head to <a href=\"http://gemini.google.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">gemini.google.com</a> and select the Pro model in the prompt bar, then ask Gemini to “show me” or “help me visualize” a complex concept so you can see for yourself.</p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <p></p>\n        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n        <div class=\" short-post__child-component \">\n         <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n         <div slot=\"uni-short-post-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"block-media_carousel\">\n           <section class=\"uni-component-spacing\">\n            <ui-carousel gap=\"24px\" analytics-module-name=\"Media Carousel\" analytics-section-header=\"The Gemini app can now generate interactive simulations and models.\" loop=\"\" active-index=\"0\">\n             <!---->\n             <div class=\"ui-carousel\" role=\"region\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\" aria-label=\"carousel\" style=\"--slides-per-view: 1; --slide-gap: 24px; --arrow-top-position: 272px;\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Media Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;The Gemini app can now generate interactive simulations and models.&quot;}\">\n              <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n              <button class=\"ui-carousel__arrow ui-carousel__arrow--previous\" aria-label=\"Previous item\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-43593972\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"carousel-arrow\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n              <button class=\"ui-carousel__arrow ui-carousel__arrow--next\" aria-label=\"Next item\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-43593972\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"carousel-arrow\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n              <div class=\"ui-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"ui-carousel-43593972\">\n               <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n               <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n               <!---->\n               <div class=\"ui-carousel__slide\" role=\"tabpanel\" id=\"ui-carousel-43593972-0\" data-index=\"0\">\n                <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                <ui-carousel-slide analytics-module-name=\"Media Carousel Slide\" analytics-section-header=\"The Gemini app can now generate interactive simulations and models.\" aspect-ratio=\"horizontal\" text-alignment=\"center\" headline=\"\" read-more=\"\">\n                 <!---->\n                 <div class=\" ui-carousel-slide \">\n                  <div class=\"ui-carousel-slide__component-background\">\n                   <div class=\" ui-carousel-slide__component \">\n                    <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                    <div slot=\"content-block\" style=\"display: block;\">\n                     <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"\" alt-text=\"Text reading 'Visualize how fractals work' written into an AI prompt box\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"The Gemini app can now generate interactive simulations and models.\" autoplay=\"true\">\n                      <!---->\n                      <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width-- \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;The Gemini app can now generate interactive simulations and models.&quot;}\">\n                       <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                       <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                       <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n                        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                        <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n                         <img alt=\"Text reading 'Visualize how fractals work' written into an AI prompt box\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1_Visualize_how_fractals_work.width-1000.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1_Visualize_how_fractals_work.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/1_Visualize_how_fractals_work.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\" class=\"lazy-image--no-blur\">\n                        </div>\n                        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                        <!--?-->\n                        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                        <!--?-->\n                        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                        <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                        <!--?-->\n                       </div>\n                       <!--?-->\n                       <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                       <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                       <!--?-->\n                      </div>\n                     </uni-image-full-width>\n                    </div>\n                    <slot></slot>\n                   </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n                 </div>\n                </ui-carousel-slide>\n               </div>\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <!--?-->\n              </div>\n              <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n              <div class=\"ui-carousel__navigation\" role=\"tablist\">\n               <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n               <!---->\n               <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" class=\" ui-carousel__navigation-button ui-carousel__navigation-button--active \" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-43593972-0\" tabindex=\"0\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" class=\" ui-carousel__navigation-button \" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-43593972-1\" tabindex=\"-1\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" class=\" ui-carousel__navigation-button \" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-43593972-2\" tabindex=\"-1\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" class=\" ui-carousel__navigation-button \" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-43593972-3\" tabindex=\"-1\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Jump to position 4</button>\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" class=\" ui-carousel__navigation-button \" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-43593972-4\" tabindex=\"-1\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Jump to position 5</button>\n               <!---->\n               <!---->\n               <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" class=\" ui-carousel__navigation-button \" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-43593972-5\" tabindex=\"-1\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Jump to position 6</button>\n               <!---->\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </ui-carousel>\n           </section>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"short-post__footnotes\">\n         <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n         <div slot=\"uni-short-post-footnotes-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <uni-footnotes>\n           <!---->\n           <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n           <div class=\"uni-window uni-window__popup uni-window-popover\">\n            <div class=\"uni-window__content uni-window__popup__content uni-window-popover__content\">\n             <button class=\"uni-window__close\" aria-label=\"Close\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"close_window\" custom-class=\"h-c-icon h-c-icon--color-text\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n             <button class=\"uni-window__read\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Read more</button>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n           <div id=\"footnotes\" data-component=\"uni-footnotes\" class=\" uni-footnotes \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;footnotes&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;More Information&quot;}\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n            <div class=\"uni-footnotes__wrapper\">\n             <div class=\"uni-footnotes__container\">\n              <hr>\n              <!--?lit$735867791$-->\n              <div class=\"uni-footnotes__chevron-menu\" data-ga4-analytics-accordion-click=\"{\n          &quot;accordion_header&quot;: &quot;More Information&quot;\n        }\">\n               <p class=\"uni-chevron-menu__title\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->More Information</p>\n    