div>\n     <div class=\"short-post-page__related-articles\">\n      <h2 class=\"uni-headline-5 short-post-page__related-articles-title\">Related stories</h2>\n      <ul class=\"short-post-page__related-articles-list\">\n       <li>\n        <uni-short-related-post authors=\"Rebecca Zapfel\" index=\"0\" primary-tag=\"Products - Gemini App\" summary=\"Notebooks in Gemini give you a project base that connects the Gemini app with our AI-powered research partner, NotebookLM, for an easy…\" title=\"Try notebooks in Gemini to easily keep track of projects\" url=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/gemini-app/notebooks-gemini-notebooklm/\" ga4-context=\"{\n                  &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Short Post Related articles&quot;,\n                  &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Related stories&quot;,\n                  &quot;content_type&quot;: &quot;article page&quot;\n                }\">\n         <!---->\n         <div class=\"short-post-page__related-article short-post-page__related-article--underline\">\n          <a class=\"short-post-page__related-article-link\" href=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/gemini-app/notebooks-gemini-notebooklm/\"> \n           <h3 class=\"uni-title-2 short-post-page__related-article-title\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Try notebooks in Gemini to easily keep track of projects</h3> \n           <!--?lit$735867791$--> \n           <p class=\"uni-body--small short-post-page__related-article-body\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Notebooks in Gemini give you a project base that connects the Gemini app with our AI-powered research partner, NotebookLM, for an easy…</p> \n          </a>\n         </div>\n        </uni-short-related-post>\n       </li>\n       <li>\n        <uni-short-related-post authors=\"The Keyword Team\" index=\"1\" primary-tag=\"Topics - AI\" summary=\"Here are Google’s latest AI updates from March 2026\" title=\"The latest AI news we announced in March 2026\" url=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/technology/ai/google-ai-updates-march-2026/\" ga4-context=\"{\n                  &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Short Post Related articles&quot;,\n                  &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Related stories&quot;,\n                  &quot;content_type&quot;: &quot;article page&quot;\n                }\">\n         <!---->\n         <div class=\"short-post-page__related-article short-post-page__related-article--underline\">\n          <a class=\"short-post-page__related-article-link\" href=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/technology/ai/google-ai-updates-march-2026/\"> \n           <h3 class=\"uni-title-2 short-post-page__related-article-title\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->The latest AI news we announced in March 2026</h3> \n           <!--?lit$735867791$--> \n          </a>\n         </div>\n        </uni-short-related-post>\n       </li>\n       <li>\n        <uni-short-related-post authors=\"\" index=\"2\" primary-tag=\"Products - Gemini App\" summary=\"Gemini Drops is our regular monthly update on how to get the most out of the Gemini app.\" title=\"Find out what’s new in the Gemini app in March's Gemini Drop.\" url=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/gemini-app/gemini-drop-updates-march-2026/\" ga4-context=\"{\n                  &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Short Post Related articles&quot;,\n                  &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Related stories&quot;,\n                  &quot;content_type&quot;: &quot;Short Post&quot;\n                }\">\n         <!---->\n         <div class=\"short-post-page__related-article short-post-page__related-article--underline\">\n          <a class=\"short-post-page__related-article-link\" href=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/gemini-app/gemini-drop-updates-march-2026/\"> \n           <h3 class=\"uni-title-2 short-post-page__related-article-title\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Find out what’s new in the Gemini app in March's Gemini Drop.</h3> \n           <!--?lit$735867791$--> \n          </a>\n         </div>\n        </uni-short-related-post>\n       </li>\n       <li>\n        <uni-short-related-post authors=\"Maryam Sanglaji\" index=\"3\" primary-tag=\"Products - Gemini App\" summary=\"The Gemini app just made it easier to switch from another AI chat app, without starting from scratch.\" title=\"Make the switch: Bring your AI memories and chat history to Gemini\" url=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/gemini-app/switch-to-gemini-app/\" ga4-context=\"{\n                  &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Short Post Related articles&quot;,\n                  &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Related stories&quot;,\n                  &quot;content_type&quot;: &quot;article page&quot;\n                }\">\n         <!---->\n         <div class=\"short-post-page__related-article\">\n          <a class=\"short-post-page__related-article-link\" href=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/gemini-app/switch-to-gemini-app/\"> \n           <h3 class=\"uni-title-2 short-post-page__related-article-title\"><!--?lit$735867791$-->Make the switch: Bring your AI memories and chat history to Gemini</h3> \n           <!--?lit$735867791$--> \n          </a>\n         </div>\n        </uni-short-related-post>\n       </li>\n      </ul>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </main>\n  <div class=\"uni-newsletter-toast\" data-component=\"uni-newsletter-toast\" data-component-initialized=\"true\" style=\"bottom: -63.0938px;\">\n   <div class=\"h-c-page\">\n    <div class=\"uni-newsletter-toast--container h-c-grid\">\n     <div class=\"uni-newsletter-toast__info h-c-grid__col h-c-grid__col--12  h-c-grid__col-l--9 h-c-grid__col--align-middle\">\n      <div class=\"uni-newsletter-toast__img\">\n       <img src=\"https://blog.google/static/blogv2/images/newsletter_toast.svg?version=pr20260319-1641\" alt=\"\">\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"uni-newsletter-toast__text\">Let’s stay in touch. Get the latest news from Google in your inbox.</p>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"uni-newsletter-toast__buttons h-c-grid__col h-c-grid__col--8 h-c-grid__col-l--3\">\n      <a class=\"uni-newsletter-toast__cta uni-newsletter-toast__cta--sub\" href=\"https://blog.google/newsletter-subscribe/\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Newsletter subscribe\" data-content-type=\"blogv2 | Short Post\">Subscribe</a>\n      <button class=\"uni-newsletter-toast__cta uni-newsletter-toast__cta--no\" tabindex=\"0\" data-content-type=\"blogv2 | Short Post\">No thanks</button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google 的 Gemini 应用现已支持直接在聊天中生成交互式、功能性的模拟和 3D 模型，允许用户通过调整变量来探索复杂概念。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google 的 Gemini 应用现已支持直接在聊天中生成交互式、功能性的模拟和 3D 模型，允许用户通过调整变量来探索复杂概念。",
  "summary": "Google 对 Gemini 应用进行了更新，通过引入交互式模拟和 3D 模型，使其超越了静态文本和图表的局限。用户现在可以提示 Gemini 可视化复杂主题（如物理系统或分子结构），并进行实时交互。通过滑块和数值输入调整速度或重力等参数，用户可以观察模拟的即时变化，从而获得更具实践性的学习体验。该功能目前正向全球标准版 Gemini 应用用户推出，暂不包括教育版和 Workspace 账户。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "从静态回复向交互式模拟的转变。",
      "explanation": "Gemini 现在可以生成功能性模型，使用户能够超越阅读文本的局限，通过交互式 3D 可视化积极参与到复杂主题的学习中。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过动态参数调整实现更深层次的理解。",
      "explanation": "用户可以实时调整初速度或重力等变量，从而验证假设并观察特定输入如何影响模拟结果。"
    },
    {
      "point": "面向全球用户的广泛可访问性。",
      "explanation": "该功能正向全球所有 Gemini 应用用户推出，显著降低了获取高保真教育模拟的门槛。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Gemini 可以将你的问题和复杂主题转化为自定义的交互式可视化内容——直接在聊天中完成。",
    "无论是旋转分子还是模拟复杂的物理系统，你只需一个提示词即可进行深入探索。",
    "你可以手动调整滑块或输入精确数值来设定初速度和重力强度，并立即观察这些特定变量如何形成稳定的轨道。"
  ],
